OL,3,C85-year-old faces losing home again in
OL,4,C#2bn Ladywood regeneration
OL,6,FHe's already lived through one
OL,7,Fnightmare, now Joseph Daley fears he
OL,8,Fwon't survive another.
OL,10,FAt 85, Joseph says he's praying to die
OL,11,Fbefore being forced from the
OL,12,FBirmingham council home he's lived in
OL,13,Ffor a quarter of a century.
OL,15,FIt's not just bricks and mortar. It's
OL,16,Fthe place he rebuilt his life after
OL,17,Ffleeing volcanic destruction in
OL,18,FMontserrat.
OL,20,FNow, the bulldozers are coming again.
