OL,3,C85-year-old faces losing home again in
OL,4,C#2bn Ladywood regeneration
OL,6,FLadywood, the inner-city neighbourhood
OL,7,Fhe calls home, is at the heart of a
OL,8,F#2.2 billion regeneration scheme that
OL,9,Fpromises shiny new homes, green
OL,10,Fspaces, jobs, and investment.
OL,12,FBut for the thousands who live here
OL,13,Fnow, it's not clear what, if anything,
OL,14,Fthey'll get to keep.
OL,16,F"It's not easy to work all your life
OL,17,Fand lose all you've got," Joseph says
OL,18,Fquietly.
