OL,3,C85-year-old faces losing home again in
OL,4,C#2bn Ladywood regeneration
OL,6,F"But we were grateful to know that we
OL,7,Fhave a mother country that considered
OL,8,Fus, so we came to England."
OL,10,FHis flat is filled with Caribbean
OL,11,Ftouches, a tribute to the island life
OL,12,Fhe left behind. The thought of losing
OL,13,Fthis second home is too much.
OL,15,F"Moving would be like putting me in my
OL,16,Fgrave," he says. "You take me from
OL,17,Fdevastation, then you move me to
OL,18,Fgreater devastation. I just pray that
OL,19,FGod might move me out before they
OL,20,Fcome."
