OL,3,C85-year-old faces losing home again in
OL,4,C#2bn Ladywood regeneration
OL,6,FIn the middle of this brewing storm,
OL,7,Fdeveloper St Joseph, the firm leading
OL,8,Fthe Ladywood overhaul, has announced a
OL,9,Fnew Community Hub on Botany Walk.
OL,11,FThe idea is to offer support, host
OL,12,Flocal charities and act as a base for
OL,13,Fthe project team as the regeneration
OL,14,Fgears up.
OL,16,FThey've promised to upgrade the old
OL,17,Fcouncil neighbourhood office into a
OL,18,Fflexible 5,000 square foot space.
