OL,3,C85-year-old faces losing home again in
OL,4,C#2bn Ladywood regeneration
OL,6,FLocal lifeline Ladywood Community
OL,7,FProject, which has supported thousands
OL,8,Fof residents for nearly 40 years, will
OL,9,Fbe the first tenant through the door.
OL,11,FStephen Kirwan, Managing Director of
OL,12,FSt Joseph, insists the Hub is more
OL,13,Fthan a token gesture.
OL,15,F"Our new Community Hub at Botany Walk
OL,16,Fwill be a modern, multipurpose space
OL,17,Ffor local people," he said.
OL,19,F"We're working with the Ladywood
OL,20,FCommunity Project to make sure they
OL,21,Fcan carry on their vital work."
