OL,6,FBut on the estate, there's still a
OL,7,Fstrong sense of scepticism and pain.
OL,8,FMany feel shut out of the process,
OL,9,Fwith little information and even less
OL,10,Fsay.
OL,12,FCaron Hallahan from Ladywood Community
OL,13,FProject admits it's been a rocky road.
OL,15,F"After a worrying time, this
OL,16,Fcommitment by St Joseph means we, and
OL,17,Fothers, can continue our work," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
