OL,6,F"It was important to us to remain in
OL,7,Fthe centre of Ladywood and be a
OL,8,Fconstant, visible presence for anyone
OL,9,Fwho needs help."
OL,11,FWork won't start for several years,
OL,12,Fbut in the meantime, residents have
OL,13,Flots of questions.
OL,15,FIt's not just homes at risk but houses
OL,16,Fof worship too, such as the Ladywood
OL,17,FMethodist Church.
