OL,6,FPreacher Robert Brenchley says he is
OL,7,Fangry about potentially being forced
OL,8,Fto share a space in the new
OL,9,Fdevelopment.
OL,11,FHe said: "I've been here since 1987. I
OL,12,Fcame up from Cornwall, looked around
OL,13,Ffor a church, found one I liked, moved
OL,14,Finto the area, and I've been here ever
OL,15,Fsince.
