OL,6,F"They were suggesting demolishing the
OL,7,Fchurches and replacing us with secular
OL,8,Fcommunity space, which is appalling
OL,9,Fthat we'd have to compete with other
OL,10,Fgroups to book space or use somebody
OL,11,Felse's space, when currently we've got
OL,12,Four own.
OL,14,F"It would completely destroy
OL,15,Feverything we are trying to do, there
OL,16,Fis nothing else in the area that would
OL,17,Freplicate this one. It's
OL,18,Firreplaceable."
