OL,6,FBirmingham City Council says it is
OL,7,Fsupporting residents. Cllr Sharon
OL,8,FThompson said: "I totally understand
OL,9,Fhow difficult it is for people that
OL,10,Fare going through disruption, and that
OL,11,Fis why we are trying to make sure that
OL,12,Fwe minimise the amount of disruption
OL,13,Fthat takes place.
OL,15,F"There is a communication point that
OL,16,Fthe council needs to take up and will
OL,17,Fbe taking up.
