OL,6,F"We have not decided on what exactly
OL,7,Fwhich properties are going and which
OL,8,Fare not, as I said understand how
OL,9,Fpeople feel, I've lived through
OL,10,Fregeneration and I've lived in Lee
OL,11,FBank, so I totally get what that means
OL,12,Fand that is why we need to make sure
OL,13,Fthat we are working hand and glove
OL,14,Fwith local residents so they do have a
OL,15,Fvoice but also that we can put to bed
